    <h1 class="contentH1">Course Content</h1>
<ul class="contentp">
    <li>Introduction - importance of Phlebotomy in patient care</li>

    <li>Patient interaction and related legal, ethical and safety issues</li>

    <li>Patient identification and lab requisition form</li>

